Title: Tissot Wristwatch, Gents, Manual Wind, Gold Plated
Description: Toggle navigation Menu Home About Us View Feedback Description Summary Tissot Wristwatch, Gents, Manual Wind, Gold Plated Main Description REF:60E Wonderful clean condition pre-owned gents manual wind Tissot wristwatch with original case. Gold plated case with stainless steel back. In perfect working order and keeping perfect time. The strap is a recent replacement and not the original Tissot one. This is a watch we do not have the tools for to enable us to open to show the movement. Excluding the crown it measures approx 33mm across its facia. a few very very minor scuffs to the glass but otherwise a super clean fully working example which is ready to wear.
